            Yes, we could do a lot more to make this place more accessible, and some of it would be fairly simple. It seems extraordinary that a full list of draft Bills is not
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_16wh' title='Col. 16WH &mdash; HC Deb 24 February 2004 vol 418 c16WH' name='column_16wh' href='#column_16wh' rel='bookmark'>16WH</a>
